import {WiDaySunny, WiDayCloudy, WiDayCloudyWindy,WiDayRain, WiDaySnow,WiDayLightning, WiThermometer, WiFahrenheit, WiCelsius} from "react-icons/wi"

const weatherIcons = {
  "sunny": WiDaySunny,
  "cloudy": WiDayCloudy,
  "windy": WiDayCloudyWindy,
  "rain": WiDayRain,
  "snow": WiDaySnow,
  "lightning": WiDayLightning,
  "thermometer": WiThermometer,
  "fahrenheit": WiFahrenheit,
  "celsius": WiCelsius
}


export default weatherIcons
